======== Grid ===========
---- check resource status
crsctl stat res -t

---- check overview cluster service status
crsctl check crs

---- start/stop cluster
crsctl start/stop crs

----- add/delete node_name to/of cluster
crsctl add/delete node -n <node_name>

------ check software version 
crsctl query crs softwareversion -all

------ check vote disk status
crsctl query css votedisk

======== RAC ============
---- start/stop/check instance ORCL1 of cluster instance ORCL 
srvctl start/stop/status instance -db ORCL -i ORCL1

---- start/stop/check cluster instance on both node
srvctl start/stop/status database -db ORCL

---- check configure cluster/instance/scan
srvctl config database/listener/scan -db orcl

---- start/stop/check listener
srvctl start/stop/status listener -l listener -n node1
